\SM[double]\SE[19]Congratulations on clearing it!! \.You have
conquered this shitty game! \!\SE[0]Thank you for playing...!!

\SE[56]So, umm... \.Did you play until the end and, how was it?
\!\SE[63]I hope it was properly made...

\SE[91]Hmm, you're asking a difficult question... \SE[20]But if I
were to express my impressions regardless...

\SE[50]It was refreshing to have a sensation of peering into the
'perspective' of another person. \SE[7]I was able to have a
'valuable experience' of touching the 'world' that is seen by
someone who is not sane in their everyday life.

\SM[nod]\SE[17]I see...! \.To relive someone else's life...!!
\!\SE[15]That's the essence of a game...!?

\SE[20]You're strangely clever, aren't you...? \SE[19]It's hard
to believe that these are the words of the person who created
that....

\SE\SE[12]I see...! Thanks to Vega, I was able to gain new
insights...! \SE[12]I would definitely like to request another
test play!!

\SE[13]As a reward for helping me with the test play, I'll give
you a prize from me!! \!\SE[18]Feel free to accept it without
hesitation...!
\SE[1]Then, I'll let you out of the game!
